rison with the experiment. It is shown that the three-magnon excitations\nas well as the two-magnon excitations give rise to the intensity in the high\nenergy side of the one-magnon peak, making the spectral shape asymmetric with\nwide width, in good agreement with the experiment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2011 05:26:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2011 09:14:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-30"}
